text: Gstadt am Chiemsee (Central Bavarian: Gstod am Cheamsee) is a municipality in Rosenheim, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. == Municipal parts == * Gollenshausen * Gstadt * Aich * Aiglsbuch * Aisching * Ed * Lienzing * Lienzinger Moos * Loiberting * Mitterndorf * Plötzing * Preinersdorf * Schalchen * Söll * Weingarten == References == Category:Municipalities in Bavaria Category:Rosenheim (district)
